WEBVTT

00:00:05.806 --> 00:00:08.141 line:80%
[♪ pop music playing]

00:00:50.058 --> 00:00:53.770 line:80%
PERFECT CROWN

00:01:04.656 --> 00:01:05.782 line:80%
THIS IS A WORK OF FICTION

00:01:05.866 --> 00:01:07.784 line:80%
CHILD ACTORS AND ANIMALS
WERE FILMED SAFELY

00:01:08.451 --> 00:01:09.452 line:20%
EPISODE 11

00:01:09.536 --> 00:01:10.537 line:20%
[phone buzzing]

00:01:10.620 --> 00:01:12.914 line:20%
Your Royal Highness,
it is the Queen Mother.

00:01:15.876 --> 00:01:17.127 line:20%
[phone buzzes]

00:01:19.963 --> 00:01:22.841 line:20%
[Jeongwoo] <i>I'd like a brief audience</i>
<i>in the Council Hall.</i>

00:01:22.924 --> 00:01:25.176 line:20%
Do we have time
before we're due at the Throne Hall?

00:01:25.260 --> 00:01:26.636 line:20%
Well…

00:01:27.637 --> 00:01:30.056 line:20%
Yes, we have about 30 minutes.

00:01:30.932 --> 00:01:32.142 line:20%
Right.

00:01:34.144 --> 00:01:35.228 line:80%
[phone buzzes]

00:01:37.689 --> 00:01:38.690 line:80%
Your Royal Highness.

00:01:39.941 --> 00:01:43.528 line:80%
It seems like His Majesty wants to enter
the Throne Hall with you?

00:01:43.612 --> 00:01:44.613 line:80%
His Majesty does?

00:01:44.696 --> 00:01:46.656 line:80%
Yes. It appears he's a bit nervous.

00:01:47.991 --> 00:01:49.242 line:80%
[sighs]

00:01:50.660 --> 00:01:51.661 line:80%
I'll meet you there.

00:01:51.745 --> 00:01:53.246 line:80%
I won't be long.

00:01:54.414 --> 00:01:55.415 line:80%
Ah…

00:01:59.961 --> 00:02:01.296 line:80%
Yes, Your Royal Highness.

00:02:28.615 --> 00:02:30.367 line:80%
[explosion]

00:02:30.450 --> 00:02:32.285 line:80%
[♪ dramatic music playing]

00:02:34.079 --> 00:02:35.080 line:80%
Grand Princess.

00:02:35.705 --> 00:02:36.706 line:80%
You must flee.

00:02:37.457 --> 00:02:40.251 line:80%
Isn't that… the Council Hall?

00:02:41.044 --> 00:02:42.128 line:80%
Grand Princess.

00:02:42.629 --> 00:02:43.797 line:80%
[explosion]

00:02:53.974 --> 00:02:54.975 line:80%
No…

00:02:57.018 --> 00:02:58.603 line:80%
No! [gasps]

00:02:58.687 --> 00:02:59.854 line:80%
[Hyeon] Your Highness!

00:03:08.029 --> 00:03:09.572 line:80%
What was that?

00:03:11.199 --> 00:03:13.201 line:80%
Go and see what happened.

00:03:13.284 --> 00:03:14.327 line:80%
[gasps]

00:03:14.411 --> 00:03:15.704 line:80%
Yes, Your Majesty.

00:03:19.374 --> 00:03:22.002 line:80%
[clamoring]

00:03:29.718 --> 00:03:32.303 line:80%
-[Hyejeong panting]
-[staff shrieks]

00:03:39.269 --> 00:03:40.437 line:80%
Aide Do.

00:03:40.520 --> 00:03:41.730 line:80%
What…

00:03:43.815 --> 00:03:45.066 line:80%
What are you doing here?

00:03:46.568 --> 00:03:47.986 line:80%
[exhales sharply]

00:03:51.406 --> 00:03:52.615 line:80%
Tell me.

00:03:56.286 --> 00:03:57.537 line:80%
Do Hyejeong!

00:03:57.620 --> 00:03:58.997 line:80%
[gasps] The Council Hall…

00:04:02.000 --> 00:04:03.084 line:80%
His Royal Highness.

00:04:04.127 --> 00:04:06.212 line:80%
He's in the Council Hall. [panting]

00:04:06.838 --> 00:04:07.922 line:80%
[gasps]

00:04:25.732 --> 00:04:26.733 line:80%
Your Royal Highness.

00:04:29.778 --> 00:04:30.779 line:80%
No!

00:04:30.862 --> 00:04:32.489 line:80%
-Grand Princess!
-Ms. Seong!

00:04:33.406 --> 00:04:35.116 line:80%
[Hyeon] You can't, Grand Princess!

00:04:35.825 --> 00:04:39.746 line:80%
-[exclaims]
-[screaming]

00:04:44.167 --> 00:04:46.795 line:80%
PERFECT CROWN

00:04:49.798 --> 00:04:51.841 line:80%
[coughs]

00:04:54.469 --> 00:04:55.470 line:80%
[grunts]

00:04:57.639 --> 00:04:58.640 line:80%
[groans]

00:04:59.349 --> 00:05:00.517 line:80%
Is anyone…

00:05:00.600 --> 00:05:02.185 line:80%
Is anyone out there?

00:05:02.268 --> 00:05:04.604 line:80%
-[coughs]
-[Huiju] Your Royal Highness!

00:05:04.687 --> 00:05:08.066 line:80%
[breathing heavily]

00:05:08.691 --> 00:05:09.692 line:80%
[exclaims]

00:05:13.196 --> 00:05:15.573 line:80%
[coughs]

00:05:15.657 --> 00:05:16.658 line:80%
[sniffles]

00:05:17.242 --> 00:05:18.243 line:80%
Your Royal Highness!

00:05:18.827 --> 00:05:20.203 line:80%
Your Royal Highness!

00:05:20.286 --> 00:05:21.371 line:80%
[pants]

00:05:30.255 --> 00:05:32.507 line:80%
If something terrible happens to you…

00:05:34.634 --> 00:05:35.760 line:80%
[I-AN] <i>You can't…</i>

00:05:40.473 --> 00:05:41.891 line:80%
[Huiju] <i>Let's see this through.</i>

00:05:45.728 --> 00:05:47.272 line:80%
I will be by your side.

00:05:50.483 --> 00:05:51.526 line:80%
[sighs]

00:05:52.402 --> 00:05:54.279 line:80%
[panting]

00:05:58.283 --> 00:05:59.284 line:80%
[I-AN] <i>Don't come.</i>

00:06:00.869 --> 00:06:01.870 line:80%
Your Royal Highness!

00:06:03.663 --> 00:06:05.165 line:80%
[breathing heavily]

00:06:10.044 --> 00:06:12.046 line:80%
Your Royal Highness! [gasps]

00:06:13.298 --> 00:06:14.841 line:80%
Your Royal Highness… [winces]

00:06:15.758 --> 00:06:16.801 line:80%
[groans]

00:06:20.763 --> 00:06:21.890 line:80%
[grunts]

00:06:24.767 --> 00:06:25.852 line:80%
Your Royal Highness.

00:06:27.061 --> 00:06:28.062 line:80%
Your Royal Highness!

00:06:28.146 --> 00:06:29.230 line:80%
[shrieks]

00:06:35.570 --> 00:06:37.488 line:80%
[gasps] Your Royal Highness.

00:06:38.823 --> 00:06:39.991 line:80%
Your Royal Highness.

00:06:40.074 --> 00:06:42.285 line:80%
Your Royal Highness, you need to wake up.

00:06:42.368 --> 00:06:44.370 line:80%
[sniffles, pants]

00:06:46.581 --> 00:06:48.499 line:80%
[grunts]

00:06:51.836 --> 00:06:53.004 line:80%
Your Royal Highness.

00:06:58.718 --> 00:07:01.221 line:80%
[heart beating]

00:07:06.684 --> 00:07:08.061 line:80%
[sighs]

00:07:09.229 --> 00:07:10.647 line:80%
Your Royal Highness.

00:07:12.649 --> 00:07:14.484 line:80%
I'll get you out of here.

00:07:14.567 --> 00:07:15.652 line:80%
[pants, sniffles]

00:07:18.071 --> 00:07:19.155 line:80%
[grunting]

00:07:24.160 --> 00:07:25.370 line:80%
[strains]

00:07:30.708 --> 00:07:31.709 line:80%
[strains]

00:07:33.461 --> 00:07:34.462 line:80%
[pants]

00:07:37.340 --> 00:07:38.341 line:80%
Your Royal Highness.

00:07:38.424 --> 00:07:41.594 line:80%
Your Royal Highness, please wake up.

00:07:45.223 --> 00:07:47.350 line:80%
[sobbing] Someone, please save him.

00:07:47.433 --> 00:07:49.894 line:80%
Is anyone out there?

00:07:51.271 --> 00:07:53.314 line:80%
Is there anyone out there?

00:07:59.696 --> 00:08:02.073 line:80%
Please help us… [crying]

00:08:03.866 --> 00:08:04.867 line:80%
Your Royal Highness.

00:08:05.827 --> 00:08:07.078 line:80%
Your Royal Highness…

00:08:11.582 --> 00:08:12.834 line:80%
[King sobbing] Mother!

00:08:13.334 --> 00:08:14.335 line:80%
Your Majesty.

00:08:14.836 --> 00:08:17.714 line:80%
Mother, there's a fire in the palace.

00:08:18.673 --> 00:08:20.008 line:80%
What is he talking about?

00:08:20.591 --> 00:08:22.593 line:80%
A fire has broken out at the Council Hall.

00:08:23.219 --> 00:08:25.555 line:80%
Uncle is… [crying]

00:08:31.602 --> 00:08:32.854 line:80%
Is I-AN safe?

00:08:33.521 --> 00:08:34.605 line:80%
Your Majesty…

00:08:35.732 --> 00:08:36.941 line:80%
Answer me!

00:08:37.984 --> 00:08:39.277 line:80%
Is I-AN safe?

00:08:53.166 --> 00:08:54.250 line:80%
[Lady Choi sighs]

00:08:56.294 --> 00:08:59.172 line:80%
You should get some rest, Grand Princess.

00:08:59.756 --> 00:09:02.008 line:80%
The royal physicians said he is stable.

00:09:03.593 --> 00:09:07.180 line:80%
How could you have just run
into the fire like that?

00:09:07.263 --> 00:09:09.265 line:80%
Had Aide Choi not reached you in time,

00:09:09.349 --> 00:09:10.475 line:80%
you would also be…

00:09:10.558 --> 00:09:12.268 line:80%
He would've come to save me.

00:09:13.686 --> 00:09:14.687 line:80%
[Lady Choi] Pardon?

00:09:16.647 --> 00:09:19.859 line:80%
If it had been me in there, he would have…

00:09:24.405 --> 00:09:25.782 line:80%
come for me too.

00:09:27.033 --> 00:09:28.159 line:80%
To save me.

00:09:31.287 --> 00:09:32.914 line:80%
Like he always has.

00:09:37.543 --> 00:09:38.795 line:80%
[inhales deeply]

00:09:39.712 --> 00:09:42.965 line:80%
Sir, you need to be announced first! Ah…

00:09:56.521 --> 00:09:58.231 line:80%
The Grand Prince is stable, so tomorrow--

00:09:58.314 --> 00:10:00.191 line:80%
How could you just run in there like that?

00:10:01.818 --> 00:10:04.695 line:80%
Lower your voice.
The palace attendants are outside.

00:10:04.779 --> 00:10:06.114 line:80%
Why aren't you at a hospital?

00:10:07.281 --> 00:10:09.784 line:80%
You should at least get proper treatment.

00:10:10.535 --> 00:10:12.662 line:80%
How can I trust any hospital right now?

00:10:12.745 --> 00:10:15.123 line:80%
-What?
-You think this fire was just an accident?

00:10:17.667 --> 00:10:20.294 line:80%
They targeted the Grand Prince
at the wedding, not me.

00:10:20.378 --> 00:10:22.630 line:80%
And now, a fire just breaks out
on abdication day?

00:10:22.713 --> 00:10:23.881 line:80%
You expect me to buy that?

00:10:24.757 --> 00:10:25.758 line:80%
[sighs]

00:10:28.052 --> 00:10:29.387 line:80%
And if it wasn't an accident?

00:10:31.305 --> 00:10:33.724 line:80%
-What?
-What can you do if it wasn't?

00:10:34.642 --> 00:10:37.562 line:80%
Will you collapse and die in his place?

00:10:37.645 --> 00:10:38.646 line:80%
[scoffs]

00:10:38.729 --> 00:10:40.857 line:80%
Then what should I have done?

00:10:40.940 --> 00:10:43.401 line:80%
-Just leave him there to die?
-Yes, just leave him!

00:10:46.320 --> 00:10:47.655 line:80%
Jeongwoo.

00:10:48.239 --> 00:10:49.574 line:80%
[sighs]

00:10:53.494 --> 00:10:55.872 line:80%
How much longer
must I watch you be in danger?

00:11:00.585 --> 00:11:02.378 line:80%
How much longer must I endure this?

00:11:05.006 --> 00:11:06.799 line:80%
[breathes shakily]

00:11:14.098 --> 00:11:15.558 line:80%
[sighs]

00:11:23.816 --> 00:11:24.942 line:80%
[sighs]

00:11:25.985 --> 00:11:27.778 line:80%
I've been looking everywhere for you.

00:11:29.113 --> 00:11:30.239 line:80%
What are you doing here?

00:11:37.246 --> 00:11:38.289 line:80%
Are you okay?

00:11:41.751 --> 00:11:42.793 line:80%
Yes.

00:11:42.877 --> 00:11:43.920 line:80%
[sighs, chuckles]

00:11:44.754 --> 00:11:47.548 line:80%
I'm told the Grand Prince
and Princess are both fine.

00:11:47.632 --> 00:11:49.383 line:80%
You don't need to worry too much.

00:11:52.553 --> 00:11:53.554 line:80%
[sighs]

00:11:58.059 --> 00:12:00.561 line:80%
[cries] I'm sorry.

00:12:00.645 --> 00:12:03.022 line:80%
What? Why are you apologizing?

00:12:05.107 --> 00:12:06.108 line:80%
I mean…

00:12:06.192 --> 00:12:07.193 line:80%
[sniffles]

00:12:08.319 --> 00:12:09.320 line:80%
[sighs]

00:12:09.403 --> 00:12:11.989 line:80%
I should've never left
the Grand Prince's side, right?

00:12:12.073 --> 00:12:13.407 line:80%
Wait, come on now.

00:12:13.491 --> 00:12:16.160 line:80%
It's not like your being there

00:12:16.244 --> 00:12:18.412 line:80%
would've magically stopped
the fire from starting.

00:12:18.496 --> 00:12:20.164 line:80%
[chuckles] Come on, that's silly.

00:12:26.837 --> 00:12:29.799 line:80%
Wait, hold on. Do you really believe that?

00:12:29.882 --> 00:12:30.967 line:80%
[sighs]

00:12:31.050 --> 00:12:33.052 line:80%
[breathes shakily]

00:12:43.354 --> 00:12:44.438 line:80%
Thank you.

00:12:45.147 --> 00:12:46.148 line:80%
What?

00:12:47.441 --> 00:12:49.026 line:80%
-[Hyeon] Grand Princess!
-[Hyejeong] Ms. Seong!

00:12:49.110 --> 00:12:50.653 line:80%
[Hyeon] You can't, Grand Princess!

00:12:51.654 --> 00:12:53.322 line:80%
-[exclaims]
-[screaming]

00:12:54.323 --> 00:12:56.325 line:80%
[panting]

00:12:58.661 --> 00:12:59.662 line:80%
I'll be right back.

00:12:59.745 --> 00:13:01.163 line:80%
What? Where are you going?

00:13:01.247 --> 00:13:02.665 line:80%
-No, you can't!
-[staff screaming]

00:13:02.748 --> 00:13:05.418 line:80%
Aide Choi! Choi Hyeon!

00:13:05.501 --> 00:13:07.795 line:80%
[panting]

00:13:16.554 --> 00:13:17.597 line:80%
A royal physician!

00:13:17.680 --> 00:13:19.098 line:80%
Summon a royal physician!

00:13:19.181 --> 00:13:20.891 line:80%
[clamoring]

00:13:23.686 --> 00:13:25.438 line:80%
[exclaims, gasps]

00:13:25.521 --> 00:13:26.647 line:80%
Thank goodness…

00:13:27.565 --> 00:13:28.858 line:80%
Thank goodness.

00:13:35.406 --> 00:13:37.158 line:80%
If it weren't for you, they would both be…

00:13:37.241 --> 00:13:38.242 line:80%
Oh.

00:13:38.868 --> 00:13:40.578 line:80%
[stammers] Stop that.

00:13:40.661 --> 00:13:43.247 line:80%
I mean, I was just doing my job.

00:13:44.081 --> 00:13:45.708 line:80%
[♪ soft piano music playing]

00:13:52.423 --> 00:13:53.507 line:80%
I was worried…

00:13:55.468 --> 00:13:56.677 line:80%
that you'd get hurt.

00:14:21.243 --> 00:14:22.244 line:80%
Thank you.

00:14:24.413 --> 00:14:25.414 line:80%
But you know,

00:14:25.998 --> 00:14:27.333 line:80%
I just got all better.

00:14:28.417 --> 00:14:29.502 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:14:30.836 --> 00:14:32.630 line:80%
Oh, ow, ow… Hold on. Ow…

00:14:32.713 --> 00:14:34.006 line:80%
Are you okay?

00:14:34.840 --> 00:14:37.301 line:80%
It's so itchy right here.
Can you scratch it for me?

00:14:37.385 --> 00:14:38.511 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:14:38.594 --> 00:14:40.513 line:80%
Why are you crying?

00:14:40.596 --> 00:14:41.722 line:80%
Don't cry.

00:14:41.806 --> 00:14:44.266 line:80%
Crying one second and laughing the next?

00:14:44.850 --> 00:14:46.686 line:80%
-Just pick one already.
-[chuckles]

00:14:46.769 --> 00:14:48.020 line:80%
You're no crybaby.

00:14:48.104 --> 00:14:50.314 line:80%
Where are all these tears coming from?
Huh?

00:14:56.404 --> 00:14:57.571 line:80%
[sighs]

00:14:58.197 --> 00:14:59.198 line:80%
[door opens]

00:15:00.116 --> 00:15:01.742 line:80%
What's wrong? Are you feeling unwell?

00:15:01.826 --> 00:15:03.536 line:80%
Should we go to the hospital?

00:15:03.619 --> 00:15:04.620 line:80%
Why was he…

00:15:06.080 --> 00:15:07.957 line:80%
at the Council Hall today?

00:15:08.040 --> 00:15:10.251 line:80%
He was due to accept
the abdication in the Throne Hall.

00:15:11.043 --> 00:15:12.044 line:80%
Oh…

00:15:12.795 --> 00:15:14.964 line:80%
Prime Minister Min texted,
asking for a quick chat

00:15:15.047 --> 00:15:16.215 line:80%
at the Council Hall.

00:15:19.468 --> 00:15:20.720 line:80%
Jeongwoo…

00:15:22.179 --> 00:15:23.472 line:80%
had him go there?

00:15:25.349 --> 00:15:26.559 line:80%
Yes.

00:15:29.645 --> 00:15:30.980 line:80%
[sighs]

00:15:53.961 --> 00:15:55.087 line:80%
[grunts]

00:15:56.464 --> 00:15:57.506 line:80%
Your Royal Highness.

00:15:59.550 --> 00:16:00.968 line:80%
Your Royal Highness! [shrieks]

00:16:02.803 --> 00:16:04.889 line:80%
[♪ romantic music playing]

00:16:13.272 --> 00:16:14.273 line:80%
[I-AN] <i>Stay still.</i>

00:16:26.118 --> 00:16:27.661 line:80%
<i>I must appear…</i>

00:16:29.038 --> 00:16:30.414 line:80%
<i>insanely infatuated with you</i>

00:16:31.707 --> 00:16:33.125 line:80%
<i>for people to believe</i>

00:16:34.418 --> 00:16:36.128 line:80%
<i>this absurd marriage is genuine.</i>

00:16:39.006 --> 00:16:40.257 line:80%
<i>Do not bend to their will.</i>

00:16:41.967 --> 00:16:43.052 line:80%
<i>Do not back away</i>

00:16:44.762 --> 00:16:46.096 line:80%
<i>and do not compromise.</i>

00:16:50.851 --> 00:16:52.561 line:80%
<i>I shall fight with all that I have.</i>

00:16:56.690 --> 00:16:57.900 line:80%
<i>Just as you do.</i>

00:17:01.987 --> 00:17:04.156 line:80%
<i>I have a great deal that you do not…</i>

00:17:05.574 --> 00:17:07.326 line:80%
<i>and if you ask for it,</i>

00:17:08.702 --> 00:17:10.412 line:80%
<i>I fully intend to provide it.</i>

00:17:52.580 --> 00:17:54.039 line:80%
[heart beating]

00:17:55.374 --> 00:17:58.043 line:80%
I thought you said
the palace was the safest.

00:18:02.089 --> 00:18:04.925 line:80%
Is there any place safe for you?

00:18:20.691 --> 00:18:23.152 line:80%
[secretary] The Council Hall was
practically empty at the time.

00:18:23.235 --> 00:18:25.446 line:80%
For an explosion that big,
casualties are minimal.

00:18:26.196 --> 00:18:28.866 line:80%
We will make a joint statement
with the Royal Secretariat--

00:18:28.949 --> 00:18:30.242 line:80%
No need.

00:18:31.702 --> 00:18:32.703 line:80%
Just leave it for now.

00:18:33.370 --> 00:18:34.538 line:80%
Pardon?

00:18:35.706 --> 00:18:37.499 line:80%
Let's leave it until the Grand Prince…

00:18:39.001 --> 00:18:40.169 line:80%
wakes up.

00:18:43.756 --> 00:18:47.343 line:80%
<i>Last night, a major fire broke out</i>
<i>at Gyeongbokgung Palace.</i>

00:18:47.426 --> 00:18:52.473 line:80%
<i>Witnesses at Gwanghwamun Square</i>
<i>reported hearing a loud explosion.</i>

00:18:52.556 --> 00:18:55.017 line:80%
<i>With no official statement</i>
<i>from the palace yet,</i>

00:18:55.100 --> 00:18:58.062 line:80%
<i>there are growing concerns</i>
<i>over the safety of the royal family.</i>

00:18:58.145 --> 00:19:00.147 line:80%
I want the past month's CCTV footage

00:19:00.230 --> 00:19:02.524 line:80%
of the Council Hall interior,
entrance, and corridors.

00:19:02.608 --> 00:19:03.901 line:80%
Have it copied and sent over.

00:19:03.984 --> 00:19:05.611 line:80%
Is three days enough to review?

00:19:06.403 --> 00:19:07.780 line:80%
[sighs]

00:19:07.863 --> 00:19:10.616 line:80%
With Court Lady Choi, Aide Choi,

00:19:10.699 --> 00:19:13.327 line:80%
and Castle Beauty's Exec Ops on board,

00:19:13.410 --> 00:19:14.870 line:80%
we'll make it happen.

00:19:14.954 --> 00:19:18.457 line:80%
I want to question every attendant,
Royal Guard, and official

00:19:19.041 --> 00:19:21.794 line:80%
in the vicinity of the Council Hall
at the time of the incident.

00:19:21.877 --> 00:19:24.964 line:80%
[sucks teeth] Uh, that would fall
under the Inner Court's jurisdiction.

00:19:25.047 --> 00:19:26.090 line:80%
Mmm… [smacks lips]

00:19:26.173 --> 00:19:28.634 line:80%
I'll ask for cooperation
from the Queen Mother's Quarters.

00:19:30.552 --> 00:19:31.553 line:80%
No need.

00:19:32.721 --> 00:19:34.890 line:80%
I'll just ask her myself.

00:19:37.267 --> 00:19:38.394 line:80%
[sighs]

00:19:42.690 --> 00:19:44.608 line:80%
Is I-AN all right?

00:19:47.444 --> 00:19:49.822 line:80%
I wanted to visit him
at Anhwadang Hall, but…

00:19:49.905 --> 00:19:51.323 line:80%
Worried that he might actually…

00:19:52.950 --> 00:19:54.118 line:80%
pull through?

00:19:57.454 --> 00:19:59.873 line:80%
It happened as he was
about to accept the abdication.

00:20:00.791 --> 00:20:02.459 line:80%
And Your Majesty was the only one

00:20:03.085 --> 00:20:04.545 line:80%
who was against it.

00:20:05.337 --> 00:20:06.338 line:80%
[sighs]

00:20:06.422 --> 00:20:08.007 line:80%
Grand Princess, I…

00:20:08.090 --> 00:20:10.009 line:80%
If you don't want to be a suspect,

00:20:10.592 --> 00:20:12.011 line:80%
grant me unfettered access

00:20:13.137 --> 00:20:15.305 line:80%
to the palace attendants' shift records.

00:20:15.389 --> 00:20:17.057 line:80%
[♪ tense music playing]

00:20:20.978 --> 00:20:23.105 line:80%
His Royal Highness will pull through.

00:20:26.984 --> 00:20:27.985 line:80%
That's the only way…

00:20:37.161 --> 00:20:39.496 line:80%
you make it out of this unscathed.

00:20:44.752 --> 00:20:45.753 line:80%
Oh…

00:20:47.212 --> 00:20:49.548 line:80%
I'm afraid I don't accept drinks
so freely anymore.

00:21:02.102 --> 00:21:03.103 line:80%
And the investigation?

00:21:03.604 --> 00:21:04.646 line:80%
When will it begin?

00:21:04.730 --> 00:21:06.899 line:80%
The Royal Protection Branch
will start it first,

00:21:06.982 --> 00:21:09.068 line:80%
and the police will join later.

00:21:09.151 --> 00:21:10.194 line:80%
It will not be public.

00:21:11.361 --> 00:21:12.362 line:80%
Why not public?

00:21:13.655 --> 00:21:15.282 line:80%
It came from the prime minister.

00:21:15.365 --> 00:21:18.827 line:80%
With the poisoning case still open,
he wanted to keep things from escalating.

00:21:18.911 --> 00:21:20.496 line:80%
He should be at Anhwadang Hall now.

00:21:21.997 --> 00:21:23.082 line:80%
Who?

00:21:23.791 --> 00:21:25.918 line:80%
-Prime Minister Min?
-Yes.

00:21:27.836 --> 00:21:28.879 line:80%
[gasps]

00:21:34.176 --> 00:21:36.011 line:80%
[pants]

00:21:38.013 --> 00:21:39.014 line:80%
Did you run over here?

00:21:43.936 --> 00:21:45.771 line:80%
He should've been awake by now,

00:21:45.854 --> 00:21:47.356 line:80%
but I hadn't heard anything yet.

00:21:49.316 --> 00:21:50.526 line:80%
Right.

00:21:50.609 --> 00:21:54.029 line:80%
The royal physician said he's
in a near-comatose state due to stress.

00:21:54.113 --> 00:21:57.324 line:80%
It's a sign his body is recovering,
so he should be waking up soon.

00:21:58.742 --> 00:21:59.743 line:80%
When is "soon"?

00:22:01.078 --> 00:22:02.329 line:80%
Well, that is…

00:22:02.412 --> 00:22:04.873 line:80%
Apparently, there's no way of knowing.

00:22:07.084 --> 00:22:08.293 line:80%
Let's give it some time.

00:22:17.845 --> 00:22:19.388 line:80%
You didn't need to see me out.

00:22:21.431 --> 00:22:22.432 line:80%
Sorry.

00:22:25.644 --> 00:22:27.604 line:80%
Maybe it's everything
that's been going on.

00:22:28.730 --> 00:22:30.149 line:80%
I'm a little on edge.

00:22:34.945 --> 00:22:37.531 line:80%
By the way, don't you go
to the cathedral anymore?

00:22:38.824 --> 00:22:39.825 line:80%
What?

00:22:40.742 --> 00:22:42.161 line:80%
You're not wearing your rosary.

00:22:44.454 --> 00:22:46.039 line:80%
[Jeongwoo] Ah…

00:22:46.123 --> 00:22:47.749 line:80%
It gets in the way when I work.

00:22:48.250 --> 00:22:49.626 line:80%
Right.

00:22:50.711 --> 00:22:51.712 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:22:53.422 --> 00:22:54.715 line:80%
Get back safely.

00:22:55.674 --> 00:22:57.050 line:80%
Thanks. [chuckles]

00:23:05.267 --> 00:23:06.268 line:80%
[car door closes]

00:23:24.077 --> 00:23:25.078 line:80%
[Dayeong] What's wrong?

00:23:25.162 --> 00:23:27.414 line:80%
Huiju hasn't texted back yet?

00:23:28.040 --> 00:23:29.041 line:80%
No.

00:23:29.583 --> 00:23:31.460 line:80%
Let's eat. [sighs]

00:23:32.294 --> 00:23:33.378 line:80%
What should we get?

00:23:34.671 --> 00:23:35.672 line:80%
This place is known for…

00:23:35.756 --> 00:23:37.424 line:80%
-[patron] At the palace?
-Yeah.

00:23:37.925 --> 00:23:39.468 line:80%
Someone definitely died there.

00:23:40.344 --> 00:23:43.639 line:80%
Why else would they refuse
to make an official statement?

00:23:43.722 --> 00:23:44.723 line:80%
[patron] No way.

00:23:44.806 --> 00:23:46.558 line:80%
I did hear the explosion was really loud.

00:23:46.642 --> 00:23:48.560 line:80%
I read this rumor post…

00:23:49.394 --> 00:23:50.854 line:80%
It said Grand Prince I-AN…

00:23:52.397 --> 00:23:53.649 line:80%
is dead.

00:23:53.732 --> 00:23:54.942 line:80%
-Oh, this…
-[phone clatters]

00:23:55.025 --> 00:23:56.151 line:80%
[grunts]

00:23:56.902 --> 00:24:00.280 line:80%
-Babe, you need to call Huiju now.
-Okay.

00:24:01.156 --> 00:24:02.241 line:80%
-[sighs]
-[line ringing]

00:24:06.411 --> 00:24:07.746 line:80%
[sighs]

00:24:08.622 --> 00:24:09.831 line:80%
-[automated voice message]
-[grunts]

00:24:09.915 --> 00:24:12.167 line:80%
Would it kill her to pick up
on the first try?

00:24:12.251 --> 00:24:14.461 line:80%
-She's not picking up? Let me try.
-Okay.

00:24:14.962 --> 00:24:18.298 line:80%
INCOMING CALL
GREMLIN

00:24:18.382 --> 00:24:19.925 line:80%
[phone buzzing]

00:24:31.311 --> 00:24:32.312 line:80%
Sir.

00:24:33.563 --> 00:24:35.148 line:80%
I'm a little tired today.

00:24:35.232 --> 00:24:36.525 line:80%
Can we save it for tomorrow?

00:24:37.943 --> 00:24:40.737 line:80%
The Royal Secretariat wants
to release a statement.

00:24:41.905 --> 00:24:42.906 line:80%
[sighs]

00:24:45.701 --> 00:24:46.952 line:80%
The reason being?

00:24:47.035 --> 00:24:49.913 line:80%
There's a rumor circulating
that the Grand Prince has passed away.

00:24:49.997 --> 00:24:53.250 line:80%
The string of canceled public appearances
has also raised concerns.

00:24:53.333 --> 00:24:56.044 line:80%
There's even talk
the Grand Princess is in a critical state.

00:24:56.128 --> 00:24:57.587 line:80%
Hmm… [sighs]

00:24:57.671 --> 00:24:58.672 line:80%
That should be

00:24:59.589 --> 00:25:00.590 line:80%
more than enough.

00:25:11.184 --> 00:25:13.020 line:80%
What on earth are you talking about?

00:25:14.313 --> 00:25:15.480 line:80%
What do you mean, regency?

00:25:15.564 --> 00:25:18.025 line:80%
Public concern is growing
over the welfare of the Crown.

00:25:19.109 --> 00:25:21.653 line:80%
However, His Majesty is unable
to carry out state affairs.

00:25:21.737 --> 00:25:23.822 line:80%
Since the Grand Prince
remains unconscious,

00:25:23.905 --> 00:25:27.492 line:80%
it would only be fitting
for Your Majesty to step forward.

00:25:27.576 --> 00:25:29.578 line:80%
The Grand Prince will wake up soon.

00:25:30.120 --> 00:25:31.830 line:80%
-The Grand Princess said--
-That is why

00:25:31.913 --> 00:25:33.832 line:80%
I have come here in such a hurry.

00:25:38.295 --> 00:25:41.089 line:80%
Ending the Grand Prince's regency
was no simple matter.

00:25:42.132 --> 00:25:44.217 line:80%
Likewise, once Your Majesty
takes up the regency,

00:25:44.301 --> 00:25:45.927 line:80%
it will not be easily undone.

00:25:46.011 --> 00:25:47.596 line:80%
Even if the Grand Prince wakes up.

00:25:47.679 --> 00:25:49.681 line:80%
That would be a rash decision.

00:25:50.640 --> 00:25:52.309 line:80%
-There is still time--
-Your Majesty.

00:25:53.060 --> 00:25:55.312 line:80%
[♪ dramatic music plays]

00:25:56.271 --> 00:25:58.023 line:80%
If the notion bothers you so…

00:25:58.648 --> 00:26:02.277 line:80%
"Fulfill your duties to the Crown
as a representative of the people."

00:26:04.196 --> 00:26:05.739 line:80%
I can make it an official order.

00:26:12.329 --> 00:26:13.372 line:80%
So what will it be?

00:26:22.839 --> 00:26:24.132 line:80%
[Im] Your Majesty.

00:26:24.674 --> 00:26:26.468 line:80%
Grand Prince I-AN has arrived.

00:26:42.442 --> 00:26:43.693 line:80%
I-AN…

00:26:48.115 --> 00:26:51.159 line:80%
Please forgive me
for causing you concern, Your Majesty.

00:26:56.915 --> 00:26:57.916 line:80%
Did I…

00:27:00.627 --> 00:27:01.795 line:80%
cause you much distress?

00:27:13.390 --> 00:27:16.184 line:80%
SAJEONGJEON HALL WEST ENTRANCE
ACCESS LOG

00:27:17.686 --> 00:27:20.772 line:80%
[sighs] I expected there would be a lot,

00:27:20.856 --> 00:27:21.982 line:80%
but this is unreal.

00:27:22.065 --> 00:27:23.483 line:80%
Even if it's extensive,

00:27:24.234 --> 00:27:28.113 line:80%
attendants follow a strict routine,
so any irregularities will stand out.

00:27:29.322 --> 00:27:31.450 line:80%
Plus, only a few
have access to the Council Hall.

00:27:31.533 --> 00:27:32.534 line:80%
Right.

00:27:33.285 --> 00:27:34.286 line:80%
Your Royal Highness!

00:27:34.369 --> 00:27:36.788 line:80%
[pants]

00:27:36.872 --> 00:27:39.082 line:80%
-The Grand Prince is awake!
-[exclaims]

00:27:39.875 --> 00:27:40.959 line:80%
Your Royal Highness!

00:27:51.052 --> 00:27:52.137 line:80%
[gasps]

00:27:53.555 --> 00:27:54.848 line:80%
[sighs]

00:28:03.523 --> 00:28:05.901 line:80%
[♪ "Parallel" playing]

00:28:41.853 --> 00:28:43.188 line:80%
You shouldn't have been there.

00:28:44.981 --> 00:28:47.192 line:80%
-If something happened to you…
-[cries]

00:28:52.656 --> 00:28:54.366 line:80%
How could I possibly stay out…

00:28:56.451 --> 00:28:59.412 line:80%
[sniffles] …when I knew you were in there?

00:28:59.496 --> 00:29:01.331 line:80%
[crying]

00:29:02.874 --> 00:29:03.959 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:29:08.838 --> 00:29:09.839 line:80%
I'm sorry.

00:29:11.883 --> 00:29:12.926 line:80%
Forgive me.

00:29:13.760 --> 00:29:15.762 line:80%
[sobbing]

00:29:51.381 --> 00:29:52.757 line:80%
[sighs]

00:29:55.844 --> 00:29:57.053 line:80%
[sighs]

00:29:59.389 --> 00:30:01.099 line:80%
[Jeongwoo] <i>When did you wake up?</i>

00:30:01.891 --> 00:30:02.892 line:80%
Just now.

00:30:03.977 --> 00:30:05.645 line:80%
Have you seen the royal physician?

00:30:08.189 --> 00:30:09.733 line:80%
It was just a long nap.

00:30:09.816 --> 00:30:10.817 line:80%
He says I'm fine.

00:30:15.363 --> 00:30:17.657 line:80%
-[sighs]
-I'll resume my public duties at once.

00:30:17.741 --> 00:30:18.742 line:80%
Don't worry.

00:30:18.825 --> 00:30:21.661 line:80%
First, we should let you fully recover.

00:30:21.745 --> 00:30:22.746 line:80%
Prime Minister Min.

00:30:24.122 --> 00:30:26.916 line:80%
I hear rumors of my passing
are spreading outside these walls.

00:30:31.671 --> 00:30:32.922 line:80%
Now is the perfect time

00:30:34.090 --> 00:30:35.342 line:80%
to turn public opinion.

00:31:03.912 --> 00:31:05.914 line:80%
Since the Grand Prince
has regained consciousness,

00:31:07.415 --> 00:31:09.167 line:80%
it's time we tied up some loose ends.

00:31:14.464 --> 00:31:17.175 line:80%
LORD INPYEONG

00:31:21.596 --> 00:31:24.265 line:80%
[sighs]

00:31:35.902 --> 00:31:38.571 line:80%
[breathes shakily]

00:31:39.906 --> 00:31:43.159 line:80%
[sighs, pants]

00:31:56.131 --> 00:31:58.133 line:80%
Are you sure you're okay now?

00:31:58.717 --> 00:32:00.385 line:80%
I told you I'm fine.

00:32:01.553 --> 00:32:03.847 line:80%
Shall I call for
the royal physician again?

00:32:04.931 --> 00:32:07.142 line:80%
-[chuckles]
-[chuckles]

00:32:10.895 --> 00:32:11.896 line:80%
So…

00:32:12.981 --> 00:32:15.608 line:80%
why did you go see the Queen Mother
as soon as you woke up?

00:32:16.484 --> 00:32:18.069 line:80%
To see Prime Minister Min.

00:32:19.529 --> 00:32:20.655 line:80%
Jeongwoo?

00:32:20.739 --> 00:32:22.866 line:80%
With my waking being uncertain,

00:32:23.575 --> 00:32:26.661 line:80%
he would have to find someone
to take my place.

00:32:27.370 --> 00:32:28.413 line:80%
"Take your place"?

00:32:32.417 --> 00:32:35.587 line:80%
Are you saying he asked
the Queen Mother to act as regent?

00:32:38.506 --> 00:32:39.632 line:80%
So did you go there

00:32:40.216 --> 00:32:42.343 line:80%
to show them you're alive and well?

00:32:43.470 --> 00:32:45.805 line:80%
-Yeah.
-[sighs]

00:32:48.933 --> 00:32:49.934 line:80%
Listen.

00:32:51.394 --> 00:32:52.520 line:80%
How much

00:32:54.189 --> 00:32:55.398 line:80%
do you trust Jeongwoo?

00:32:55.482 --> 00:32:56.775 line:80%
That's random.

00:32:57.901 --> 00:32:59.652 line:80%
I mean, you two are friends,

00:33:00.445 --> 00:33:02.822 line:80%
but it's so impersonal
between you two sometimes.

00:33:03.490 --> 00:33:05.241 line:80%
Like that time with the contract.

00:33:06.367 --> 00:33:07.535 line:80%
[sighs]

00:33:08.995 --> 00:33:10.580 line:80%
There are times I want to punch him.

00:33:11.456 --> 00:33:12.999 line:80%
-What?
-But…

00:33:14.834 --> 00:33:16.419 line:80%
I've always trusted him.

00:33:19.047 --> 00:33:20.089 line:80%
Why?

00:33:20.173 --> 00:33:22.342 line:80%
Because I know

00:33:23.051 --> 00:33:26.596 line:80%
just as I'm bound by the Crown,
he's bound by the Cabinet.

00:33:28.556 --> 00:33:29.974 line:80%
[sighs]

00:33:34.521 --> 00:33:35.522 line:80%
Why do you ask?

00:33:35.605 --> 00:33:39.025 line:80%
Weren't you the one who said it was
only common sense to trust him?

00:33:41.194 --> 00:33:42.195 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:33:43.154 --> 00:33:44.364 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:33:44.447 --> 00:33:45.657 line:80%
Come here.

00:33:51.287 --> 00:33:52.288 line:80%
[sighs]

00:34:05.677 --> 00:34:06.845 line:80%
There he is!

00:34:06.928 --> 00:34:09.556 line:80%
[reporter] <i>The arsonist responsible</i>
<i>for the fire at Gyeongbokgung Palace</i>

00:34:09.639 --> 00:34:10.849 line:80%
<i>turned himself in last night.</i>

00:34:10.932 --> 00:34:12.559 line:80%
<i>During questioning, the suspect, Shin,</i>

00:34:12.642 --> 00:34:14.727 line:80%
<i>was identified as a member</i>
<i>of the Royal Guard.</i>

00:34:14.811 --> 00:34:16.604 line:80%
<i>An assassination suspect emerging</i>

00:34:16.688 --> 00:34:18.565 line:80%
<i>from the very force sworn</i>
<i>to protect the Crown</i>

00:34:18.648 --> 00:34:19.983 line:80%
<i>is sending shock waves nationwide.</i>

00:34:20.066 --> 00:34:21.442 line:80%
[protestor] Remove him!

00:34:21.526 --> 00:34:22.652 line:80%
[reporter] <i>He was also confirmed</i>

00:34:22.735 --> 00:34:25.280 line:20%
<i>to have protested</i>
<i>for the Grand Prince to step down.</i>

00:34:26.990 --> 00:34:27.991 line:80%
How amusing.

00:34:29.117 --> 00:34:30.618 line:80%
It's as if they timed it to my waking.

00:34:32.996 --> 00:34:36.040 line:80%
[Jung] Your Majesty,
Grand Prince I-AN has arrived.

00:34:36.124 --> 00:34:37.292 line:80%
Show him in.

00:34:41.379 --> 00:34:42.714 line:80%
Uncle!

00:34:44.591 --> 00:34:45.925 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:34:46.009 --> 00:34:47.010 line:80%
Your Majesty.

00:34:47.969 --> 00:34:49.345 line:80%
Are you well?

00:34:49.429 --> 00:34:51.556 line:80%
Yes, that is why I am here.

00:34:54.434 --> 00:34:56.644 line:80%
The fire at the Council Hall…

00:34:57.478 --> 00:35:00.732 line:80%
[breathes shakily, sobbing]

00:35:09.991 --> 00:35:14.037 line:80%
I thought you would end up like Father…

00:35:14.120 --> 00:35:15.955 line:80%
[sighs]

00:35:16.664 --> 00:35:18.333 line:80%
[I-AN] Do not think such thoughts.

00:35:19.792 --> 00:35:20.835 line:80%
I will

00:35:21.336 --> 00:35:22.921 line:80%
always be by Your Majesty's side.

00:35:37.101 --> 00:35:41.022 line:80%
I heard the Grand Prince and Princess
are to resume their public duties.

00:35:41.606 --> 00:35:43.733 line:80%
This is their chance.

00:35:43.816 --> 00:35:45.318 line:80%
They will not let it go to waste.

00:35:45.401 --> 00:35:47.862 line:80%
Compassion and pity are but fleeting.

00:35:50.031 --> 00:35:51.908 line:80%
You must stop them from resuming

00:35:51.991 --> 00:35:53.868 line:80%
until that fleeting moment passes.

00:35:53.952 --> 00:35:56.245 line:80%
What makes you think
they will listen to me?

00:35:56.746 --> 00:35:57.747 line:80%
Your Majesty!

00:36:00.541 --> 00:36:01.668 line:80%
[sighs]

00:36:03.211 --> 00:36:06.089 line:80%
The Grand Prince nearly lost
his life in a gas explosion.

00:36:07.256 --> 00:36:08.800 line:80%
Use his welfare as grounds

00:36:08.883 --> 00:36:10.969 line:80%
to keep them from resuming their duties.

00:36:17.308 --> 00:36:18.393 line:80%
Father.

00:36:23.690 --> 00:36:26.275 line:80%
How did you know the fire was caused

00:36:27.944 --> 00:36:29.529 line:80%
by a gas explosion?

00:36:35.118 --> 00:36:37.161 line:80%
What exactly are you getting at?

00:36:37.245 --> 00:36:39.706 line:80%
That fact was withheld from the public.

00:36:42.875 --> 00:36:44.627 line:80%
So how do you know about that?

00:37:05.231 --> 00:37:07.233 line:80%
[breathing shakily]

00:37:23.041 --> 00:37:24.625 line:80%
[sobbing]

00:37:28.629 --> 00:37:29.630 line:80%
[Im] Your Majesty.

00:37:30.256 --> 00:37:31.549 line:80%
What is the matter?

00:37:32.925 --> 00:37:35.344 line:80%
Your Majesty, you must steady yourself.

00:37:42.894 --> 00:37:45.021 line:80%
It appears I will not
be able to protect you.

00:37:49.859 --> 00:37:50.860 line:80%
Your Majesty…

00:37:53.404 --> 00:37:54.781 line:80%
However, I shall see to it…

00:37:57.742 --> 00:37:59.243 line:80%
that your family is kept safe.

00:37:59.911 --> 00:38:01.454 line:80%
[gasps]

00:38:02.288 --> 00:38:04.123 line:80%
Your grace is boundless, Your Majesty.

00:38:13.007 --> 00:38:16.677 line:80%
[breathes deeply]

00:38:16.761 --> 00:38:17.762 line:80%
[Huiju] <i>Seriously?</i>

00:38:18.346 --> 00:38:21.265 line:80%
How could one measly royal guard
blow up the Council Hall by himself?

00:38:21.349 --> 00:38:22.600 line:80%
My thoughts exactly.

00:38:23.101 --> 00:38:26.395 line:80%
The Royal Protection Branch is looking
for accomplices and co-conspirators--

00:38:26.479 --> 00:38:28.689 line:80%
-I need to leave the palace.
-Leave the palace?

00:38:31.442 --> 00:38:32.443 line:80%
[sighs]

00:38:36.030 --> 00:38:38.324 line:80%
[court staff] Your Royal Highness,
the Queen Mother has arrived.

00:38:43.663 --> 00:38:44.664 line:80%
Show her in.

00:38:49.877 --> 00:38:51.838 line:80%
[♪ ominous music plays]

00:38:55.675 --> 00:38:56.676 line:80%
You may leave.

00:39:10.773 --> 00:39:11.816 line:80%
What brings you here?

00:39:13.568 --> 00:39:14.735 line:80%
Your Majesty.

00:39:16.028 --> 00:39:17.029 line:80%
Please stand up.

00:39:17.113 --> 00:39:18.114 line:80%
I have come…

00:39:19.532 --> 00:39:21.159 line:80%
to report a grave offense.

00:39:31.377 --> 00:39:32.420 line:80%
My father…

00:39:34.755 --> 00:39:36.757 line:80%
is trying to kill you.

00:39:43.806 --> 00:39:46.392 line:80%
This is the evidence
from the incident on your wedding day.

00:39:56.611 --> 00:39:58.487 line:80%
PERSONAL DETAILS: LEE AREUM

00:39:58.571 --> 00:40:01.324 line:80%
I also have the girl who used to work
at your private residence.

00:40:01.991 --> 00:40:03.367 line:80%
She has sworn to testify.

00:40:07.997 --> 00:40:09.874 line:80%
What is your intent in reporting this?

00:40:11.792 --> 00:40:13.169 line:80%
The recent fire…

00:40:17.131 --> 00:40:18.966 line:80%
It was likely my father's doing.

00:40:21.260 --> 00:40:22.386 line:80%
So?

00:40:23.471 --> 00:40:24.805 line:80%
Are you here to beg

00:40:25.848 --> 00:40:26.891 line:80%
for his forgiveness?

00:40:26.974 --> 00:40:28.601 line:80%
I am asking you to exact punishment.

00:40:31.270 --> 00:40:32.563 line:80%
Punish me…

00:40:36.317 --> 00:40:37.443 line:80%
and my father.

00:40:49.413 --> 00:40:50.498 line:80%
[scoffs]

00:40:53.125 --> 00:40:54.794 line:80%
Did you believe me incapable of it?

00:40:55.962 --> 00:40:57.380 line:80%
And should I choose to do so…

00:40:59.548 --> 00:41:01.175 line:80%
are you sure you can handle it?

00:41:02.051 --> 00:41:03.761 line:80%
[♪ dramatic music playing]

00:41:11.519 --> 00:41:12.770 line:80%
I shall try.

00:41:16.023 --> 00:41:17.191 line:80%
[gunshot]

00:41:27.118 --> 00:41:28.286 line:80%
[sighs]

00:41:29.954 --> 00:41:31.414 line:80%
It's almost hunting season.

00:41:32.540 --> 00:41:35.251 line:80%
Right, since harvest season is
just around the corner.

00:41:35.334 --> 00:41:38.796 line:80%
Tell them I will be declaring
hunting season this year.

00:41:40.172 --> 00:41:41.299 line:80%
And not the royal family?

00:41:43.759 --> 00:41:45.553 line:80%
The Grand Prince needs time to recover,

00:41:46.846 --> 00:41:49.223 line:80%
and the Queen Mother
does not appreciate hunting.

00:41:51.142 --> 00:41:52.727 line:80%
[Huiju] Then I'll do it.

00:41:55.646 --> 00:41:56.647 line:80%
I guess I can do it.

00:42:06.449 --> 00:42:08.367 line:80%
Is it because I am accepting
the royal edict?

00:42:10.619 --> 00:42:11.620 line:80%
Why?

00:42:15.291 --> 00:42:16.625 line:80%
Why do you fear me now?

00:42:22.590 --> 00:42:24.383 line:80%
It is not that I fear you.

00:42:30.931 --> 00:42:31.932 line:80%
I have…

00:42:36.062 --> 00:42:38.105 line:80%
a duty to protect the Crown.

00:42:40.858 --> 00:42:42.568 line:80%
Thus, I am protecting you.

00:42:43.569 --> 00:42:46.030 line:80%
I am ensuring that neither my father
nor my own greed

00:42:47.156 --> 00:42:49.325 line:80%
ever harm you or the Crown again.

00:42:52.244 --> 00:42:53.371 line:80%
[crying] So please…

00:42:58.417 --> 00:42:59.585 line:80%
[breathes shakily]

00:43:02.630 --> 00:43:03.672 line:80%
Just spare…

00:43:05.925 --> 00:43:07.093 line:80%
His Majesty.

00:43:19.772 --> 00:43:21.273 line:80%
As great as the honor once was…

00:43:23.567 --> 00:43:25.111 line:80%
so too shall your disgrace be.

00:43:27.571 --> 00:43:29.198 line:80%
In both the royal family and history,

00:43:30.574 --> 00:43:32.201 line:80%
you will forever remain a sinner.

00:43:37.373 --> 00:43:39.208 line:80%
If that is the price to spare His Majesty…

00:43:45.131 --> 00:43:46.257 line:80%
would you accept?

00:43:52.930 --> 00:43:54.140 line:80%
It is more than enough.

00:44:15.870 --> 00:44:17.663 line:80%
[Huiju sighs] But…

00:44:18.456 --> 00:44:20.583 line:80%
"hunting season" in the 21st century?

00:44:21.625 --> 00:44:22.835 line:80%
What about animal rights?

00:44:25.504 --> 00:44:26.922 line:80%
Think of it as a necessary evil.

00:44:29.091 --> 00:44:30.676 line:80%
When harmful entities multiply…

00:44:33.596 --> 00:44:35.139 line:80%
we can't protect what matters.

00:44:37.308 --> 00:44:38.601 line:80%
And who determines that?

00:44:41.020 --> 00:44:42.188 line:80%
The Crown?

00:44:45.816 --> 00:44:46.984 line:80%
[sighs]

00:44:47.067 --> 00:44:48.068 line:80%
The nation.

00:44:52.114 --> 00:44:53.115 line:80%
I see.

00:44:59.538 --> 00:45:00.539 line:80%
[sighs]

00:45:06.253 --> 00:45:08.005 line:80%
So, you decide.

00:45:10.299 --> 00:45:12.218 line:80%
[♪ tense music playing]

00:45:35.032 --> 00:45:36.200 line:80%
I saw you caught the guy.

00:45:37.409 --> 00:45:39.119 line:80%
Was he a harmful entity too?

00:46:01.058 --> 00:46:02.893 line:80%
[phone buzzing]

00:46:09.191 --> 00:46:11.485 line:80%
Hey. I'm on my way back.

00:46:13.362 --> 00:46:14.363 line:80%
You're where?

00:46:20.327 --> 00:46:21.495 line:80%
[Hyejeong sighs]

00:46:23.914 --> 00:46:25.541 line:80%
He's a little drunk.

00:46:26.417 --> 00:46:27.459 line:80%
He's drunk?

00:46:27.543 --> 00:46:31.380 line:80%
Gosh. He can't even hold his liquor…
[scoffs, smacks lips]

00:46:35.342 --> 00:46:38.137 line:80%
-Boy, I'm tired. Who wants coffee?
-[sighs]

00:46:38.220 --> 00:46:39.221 line:80%
Me.

00:46:41.599 --> 00:46:42.766 line:80%
[cat meows]

00:46:58.532 --> 00:46:59.700 line:80%
[Huiju] Your Royal Highness.

00:47:00.784 --> 00:47:02.953 line:80%
My dear wife. [chuckles]

00:47:08.417 --> 00:47:11.253 line:80%
[sighs] This is great.
I was feeling cooped up anyway.

00:47:11.754 --> 00:47:13.714 line:80%
[sighs] You were?

00:47:13.797 --> 00:47:14.798 line:80%
Yeah.

00:47:15.341 --> 00:47:17.176 line:80%
The palace is so much bigger,

00:47:17.926 --> 00:47:19.094 line:80%
but far more stifling.

00:47:21.096 --> 00:47:22.931 line:80%
Agreed. [sighs]

00:47:33.275 --> 00:47:35.027 line:80%
The Queen Mother came to see me earlier.

00:47:42.618 --> 00:47:44.119 line:80%
She told me Lord INPYEONG…

00:47:50.459 --> 00:47:51.877 line:80%
was behind the wedding incident.

00:48:02.638 --> 00:48:04.848 line:80%
Seeing her beg so desperately
to spare His Majesty…

00:48:11.814 --> 00:48:13.273 line:80%
I no longer know what I am to do.

00:48:38.048 --> 00:48:39.758 line:80%
You have such a gentle heart.

00:48:41.635 --> 00:48:42.803 line:80%
It breaks my heart.

00:48:53.188 --> 00:48:54.523 line:80%
[sighs]

00:48:59.194 --> 00:49:00.654 line:20%
THE THIRTY-THIRD KING

00:49:02.030 --> 00:49:04.742 line:80%
It will reach him this time, won't it?

00:49:06.577 --> 00:49:07.870 line:80%
I believe so.

00:49:11.248 --> 00:49:12.541 line:80%
I shall entrust it to you.

00:49:14.001 --> 00:49:15.836 line:80%
Rest assured, Your Majesty.

00:49:23.469 --> 00:49:24.470 line:80%
[door opens]

00:49:33.228 --> 00:49:34.563 line:80%
I heard you asked for me.

00:49:39.026 --> 00:49:41.028 line:80%
I wanted to commend you
for your swift arrest

00:49:41.987 --> 00:49:43.655 line:80%
of the arsonist.

00:49:44.156 --> 00:49:45.449 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:49:46.658 --> 00:49:48.035 line:80%
The police deserve the credit.

00:49:49.369 --> 00:49:52.331 line:80%
[smacks lips]
I am well aware that nothing in this realm

00:49:53.040 --> 00:49:54.041 line:80%
is beyond your reach.

00:49:57.669 --> 00:49:58.670 line:80%
However,

00:50:00.547 --> 00:50:02.299 line:80%
are you still far from concluding

00:50:05.511 --> 00:50:06.637 line:80%
the poisoning case?

00:50:11.350 --> 00:50:13.018 line:80%
Hmm… [sighs]

00:50:20.692 --> 00:50:21.902 line:80%
It won't be long now.

00:50:21.985 --> 00:50:23.904 line:80%
[♪ tense music plays]

00:50:26.615 --> 00:50:28.033 line:80%
[sighs]

00:50:31.870 --> 00:50:33.038 line:80%
[sighs]

00:50:33.997 --> 00:50:35.541 line:80%
Lord INPYEONG of the Yun Family.

00:50:38.961 --> 00:50:40.212 line:80%
He is the culprit.

00:50:41.129 --> 00:50:42.130 line:80%
In terms of punishment,

00:50:43.131 --> 00:50:44.258 line:80%
I'm still deliberating.

00:50:48.303 --> 00:50:49.596 line:80%
[Yun] <i>About Prime Minister Min…</i>

00:50:53.809 --> 00:50:54.935 line:80%
Be wary of him.

00:50:58.313 --> 00:50:59.356 line:80%
What does that mean?

00:50:59.857 --> 00:51:03.360 line:80%
He was the first
to discover my father's crimes.

00:51:07.447 --> 00:51:09.575 line:80%
-That is not possible.
-He knew everything,

00:51:10.117 --> 00:51:12.119 line:80%
but chose to keep it from you.

00:51:12.202 --> 00:51:13.912 line:80%
He would have no reason to do that.

00:51:15.622 --> 00:51:17.457 line:80%
Do you truly believe that?

00:51:19.459 --> 00:51:20.627 line:80%
[Huiju] <i>How much</i>

00:51:21.628 --> 00:51:22.838 line:80%
do you trust Jeongwoo?

00:51:26.383 --> 00:51:29.595 line:80%
[sighs] Those driven by desperate desire…

00:51:33.891 --> 00:51:36.184 line:80%
often resort to unseemly choices.

00:51:49.865 --> 00:51:51.408 line:80%
What is there to consider?

00:51:53.118 --> 00:51:55.370 line:80%
As someone who is concerned
for the Crown's welfare,

00:51:55.454 --> 00:51:56.747 line:80%
I have much to consider.

00:51:57.414 --> 00:51:59.124 line:80%
He tried to kill me.

00:51:59.207 --> 00:52:00.876 line:80%
He's also the Queen Mother's father.

00:52:00.959 --> 00:52:03.378 line:80%
-Prime Minister Min.
-And His Majesty's grandfather.

00:52:03.462 --> 00:52:05.213 line:80%
-Min Jeongwoo.
-Please!

00:52:08.508 --> 00:52:10.344 line:80%
[breathes heavily]

00:52:15.641 --> 00:52:17.476 line:80%
Stop acting like a child.

00:52:23.565 --> 00:52:24.566 line:80%
[sighs]

00:52:27.569 --> 00:52:29.154 line:80%
Lord INPYEONG will… [sighs]

00:52:30.155 --> 00:52:31.740 line:80%
…never set foot in this realm again.

00:52:31.823 --> 00:52:32.824 line:80%
He will…

00:52:36.495 --> 00:52:38.121 line:80%
carry out his sentence in this realm.

00:52:39.957 --> 00:52:41.833 line:80%
Do you wish to see the Crown crumble?

00:52:41.917 --> 00:52:43.835 line:80%
Is there any reason why it should not?

00:52:48.423 --> 00:52:49.424 line:80%
[scoffs]

00:52:52.678 --> 00:52:53.679 line:80%
The Crown…

00:52:56.348 --> 00:52:57.599 line:80%
cannot last forever.

00:53:02.354 --> 00:53:03.647 line:80%
Once I ascend the throne,

00:53:05.315 --> 00:53:06.817 line:80%
I will abolish the monarchy.

00:53:15.826 --> 00:53:16.827 line:80%
[scoffs]

00:53:26.169 --> 00:53:28.422 line:80%
You've attained
everything you ever wanted.

00:53:30.590 --> 00:53:32.467 line:80%
And now you seek freedom as well?

00:53:37.305 --> 00:53:38.306 line:80%
This freedom…

00:53:40.100 --> 00:53:41.101 line:80%
won't be mine alone.

00:54:21.183 --> 00:54:22.184 line:80%
Are you okay?

00:54:26.813 --> 00:54:28.398 line:80%
Lord INPYEONG will be arrested soon.

00:54:31.943 --> 00:54:32.944 line:80%
Did Jeongwoo

00:54:33.904 --> 00:54:34.946 line:80%
agree to it?

00:54:36.031 --> 00:54:37.032 line:80%
No.

00:54:38.784 --> 00:54:40.160 line:80%
But he'll have no other choice.

00:54:41.161 --> 00:54:42.370 line:80%
I told him I knew…

00:54:44.289 --> 00:54:45.832 line:80%
and that I would not forgive him.

00:54:54.633 --> 00:54:56.051 line:80%
[Huiju sighs]

00:54:58.929 --> 00:55:00.514 line:80%
And what you wanted to confirm?

00:55:01.431 --> 00:55:02.432 line:80%
Did you?

00:55:08.772 --> 00:55:09.773 line:80%
No.

00:55:21.910 --> 00:55:23.745 line:80%
[♪ ominous music playing]

00:55:48.019 --> 00:55:50.147 line:80%
[news anchor]
<i>The first-ever compulsory investigation</i>

00:55:50.230 --> 00:55:51.857 line:80%
<i>into a royal relative has been conducted.</i>

00:55:51.940 --> 00:55:55.110 line:80%
<i>The Royal Protection Branch and police</i>
<i>announced they have obtained evidence</i>

00:55:55.193 --> 00:55:58.572 line:80%
<i>that proves Lord INPYEONG's involvement</i>
<i>in Grand Princess Seong's poisoning.</i>

00:55:58.655 --> 00:56:01.324 line:80%
<i>Authorities raided his home</i>
<i>and a research facility affiliated</i>

00:56:01.408 --> 00:56:02.742 line:80%
<i>with the Royal Seoul Hospital.</i>

00:56:02.826 --> 00:56:04.327 line:80%
ROYAL PROTECTION BRANCH

00:56:04.411 --> 00:56:05.912 line:80%
-Look!
-There she is!

00:56:05.996 --> 00:56:08.874 line:80%
[news anchor] <i>The joint investigation task</i>
<i>force stated shipment records of a drug</i>

00:56:08.957 --> 00:56:11.668 line:80%
<i>containing the same substance</i>
<i>administered to the Grand Prince,</i>

00:56:11.751 --> 00:56:15.422 line:80%
<i>as well as a testimony from a staff member</i>
<i>at his private residence, proved decisive.</i>

00:56:15.505 --> 00:56:18.800 line:80%
<i>With a royal relative suspected</i>
<i>in an attempted murder of a royal,</i>

00:56:18.884 --> 00:56:20.969 line:80%
<i>the fallout is expected to be significant.</i>

00:56:25.515 --> 00:56:26.516 line:80%
[sighs]

00:56:30.145 --> 00:56:31.271 line:80%
[Im] Your Majesty.

00:56:32.147 --> 00:56:33.815 line:80%
His Majesty has arrived.

00:56:40.322 --> 00:56:41.489 line:80%
Mother.

00:56:50.081 --> 00:56:51.082 line:80%
Your Majesty.

00:56:52.167 --> 00:56:53.168 line:80%
Yes?

00:56:58.548 --> 00:57:00.258 line:80%
You must remain strong.

00:57:00.342 --> 00:57:01.760 line:80%
[♪ gentle music playing]

00:57:03.220 --> 00:57:04.387 line:80%
If you ever feel scared,

00:57:05.555 --> 00:57:07.515 line:80%
you should go to your uncle.

00:57:09.184 --> 00:57:10.560 line:80%
Do you understand?

00:57:12.020 --> 00:57:14.272 line:80%
Yes, Mother.

00:57:38.421 --> 00:57:39.714 line:80%
[Lord INPYEONG] Your Royal Highness.

00:57:40.382 --> 00:57:42.133 line:80%
This is a misunderstanding.

00:57:42.217 --> 00:57:44.010 line:80%
Why would I ever…

00:57:44.094 --> 00:57:45.095 line:80%
Shut…

00:57:48.098 --> 00:57:49.099 line:80%
that mouth of yours.

00:57:52.227 --> 00:57:54.312 line:80%
History will remember you as a criminal,

00:57:55.063 --> 00:57:56.064 line:80%
and the Crown

00:57:57.565 --> 00:57:58.858 line:80%
will forget you ever existed.

00:58:00.860 --> 00:58:04.072 line:80%
I am His Majesty's grandfather
and the Queen Mother's father.

00:58:04.739 --> 00:58:05.949 line:80%
You cannot treat me like--

00:58:06.032 --> 00:58:07.075 line:80%
[I-AN] Did I not ask you…

00:58:09.369 --> 00:58:11.079 line:80%
to shut that mouth of yours?

00:58:16.751 --> 00:58:18.503 line:80%
The Queen Mother was the one

00:58:19.796 --> 00:58:21.131 line:80%
who told me about your crimes.

00:58:24.759 --> 00:58:25.760 line:80%
Thus…

00:58:27.887 --> 00:58:29.347 line:80%
you should mind your conduct.

00:58:33.560 --> 00:58:35.145 line:80%
The Queen Mother's welfare…

00:58:37.689 --> 00:58:39.607 line:80%
will depend on how deeply…

00:58:42.986 --> 00:58:44.154 line:80%
you repent.

00:59:05.383 --> 00:59:06.885 line:80%
You did well, Your Royal Highness.

00:59:10.388 --> 00:59:11.639 line:80%
[sighs]

00:59:11.723 --> 00:59:13.475 line:80%
The abdication has been announced.

00:59:14.351 --> 00:59:16.853 line:80%
Public sentiment is strong,
and the foreign media is all over it,

00:59:16.936 --> 00:59:18.063 line:80%
calling it long overdue.

00:59:18.646 --> 00:59:21.191 line:80%
-Let's go to the palace.
-Yes, Your Royal Highness.

00:59:21.274 --> 00:59:22.776 line:20%
[cabinet member] Abolition?

00:59:22.859 --> 00:59:25.987 line:20%
How dare anyone suggest
to abolish the monarchy?

00:59:26.071 --> 00:59:30.450 line:80%
Why do we spend all that tax money
preserving the Crown?

00:59:30.533 --> 00:59:33.620 line:80%
Because the investment generates
enough added value to justify the cost.

00:59:33.703 --> 00:59:36.956 line:80%
If the economic and diplomatic benefits
of the Crown vanish,

00:59:37.040 --> 00:59:40.043 line:80%
who exactly will be held accountable?

00:59:40.126 --> 00:59:42.712 line:80%
The people will be up in arms about it.

00:59:42.796 --> 00:59:44.631 line:80%
I'm sure such news will have them

00:59:44.714 --> 00:59:46.257 line:80%
demanding a new king immediately.

00:59:46.341 --> 00:59:49.344 line:80%
[chattering]

00:59:50.595 --> 00:59:52.430 line:80%
That is exactly why… [sighs]

00:59:56.476 --> 00:59:58.144 line:80%
…we must make him listen.

01:00:01.189 --> 01:00:02.315 line:80%
[sighs]

01:00:22.710 --> 01:00:24.129 line:80%
[sighs]

01:00:28.716 --> 01:00:29.759 line:80%
[smacks lips]

01:00:30.969 --> 01:00:32.679 line:80%
You must be busy with the coronation.
[sighs]

01:00:33.763 --> 01:00:35.098 line:80%
The Grand Prince told me.

01:00:43.273 --> 01:00:44.774 line:80%
That you had been aware

01:00:46.818 --> 01:00:48.111 line:80%
of what Lord INPYEONG did.

01:00:51.322 --> 01:00:52.907 line:80%
[sighs]

01:00:54.826 --> 01:00:55.910 line:80%
Then what about you?

01:00:56.953 --> 01:00:58.371 line:80%
Did you know?

01:00:58.455 --> 01:01:00.582 line:80%
That he's looking to abolish the monarchy.

01:01:04.836 --> 01:01:05.837 line:80%
A king

01:01:06.921 --> 01:01:09.132 line:80%
doesn't get to do whatever he wants.

01:01:09.841 --> 01:01:11.634 line:80%
My job is to make sure he doesn't.

01:01:11.718 --> 01:01:13.136 line:80%
What if it is a necessary evil?

01:01:13.219 --> 01:01:14.429 line:80%
What?

01:01:14.512 --> 01:01:17.599 line:80%
What if, in the 21st century,
our Crown itself turns out to be

01:01:18.850 --> 01:01:19.976 line:80%
the harmful entity?

01:01:22.228 --> 01:01:23.354 line:80%
What then?

01:01:25.982 --> 01:01:27.400 line:80%
[sighs]

01:01:30.653 --> 01:01:31.738 line:80%
I already told you.

01:01:32.864 --> 01:01:35.033 line:80%
That is for the nation to decide.

01:01:44.042 --> 01:01:45.043 line:80%
It appears…

01:01:51.424 --> 01:01:52.926 line:80%
we may end up as enemies.

01:02:04.354 --> 01:02:05.855 line:80%
[drum beat]

01:02:11.945 --> 01:02:15.532 line:80%
[eunuch] Announcing His Majesty!

01:02:21.788 --> 01:02:24.332 line:80%
[♪ majestic music playing]

01:03:22.724 --> 01:03:25.268 line:80%
[eunuch] We declare!

01:03:25.351 --> 01:03:27.145 line:80%
-Long live the King!
-Long live the King!

01:03:29.981 --> 01:03:32.525 line:80%
-Long live the King!
-Long live the King!

01:03:34.652 --> 01:03:37.238 line:80%
-Long live the King!
-Long live the King!

01:03:51.461 --> 01:03:53.254 line:80%
[♪ pop music plays]

01:03:53.338 --> 01:03:56.257 line:80%
PERFECT CROWN

01:04:33.419 --> 01:04:35.672 line:80%
[eunuch] All rise
for His Majesty the King!

01:04:35.755 --> 01:04:37.840 line:80%
[royal family member] <i>Your Majesty.</i>
<i>Abolition of the monarchy?</i>

01:04:37.924 --> 01:04:40.051 line:80%
[reporter] <i>Is it true there are talks</i>
<i>of abolishing the monarchy?</i>

01:04:40.134 --> 01:04:41.886 line:80%
[Huiju] <i>You're saying the Cabinet</i>
<i>and Royal Relatives</i>

01:04:41.969 --> 01:04:43.429 line:80%
<i>will oppose it, no question?</i>

01:04:43.513 --> 01:04:46.933 line:80%
[Hyeon] <i>Most of the establishment</i>
<i>is connected to the Crown.</i>

01:04:47.016 --> 01:04:48.601 line:80%
[Jeongwoo] <i>Voice your objection there.</i>

01:04:50.061 --> 01:04:51.354 line:20%
<i>Simply hint that…</i>

01:04:51.437 --> 01:04:53.356 line:20%
<i>…is His Majesty's own pursuit.</i>

01:04:53.439 --> 01:04:54.524 line:20%
What summons?

01:04:54.607 --> 01:04:56.359 line:20%
[Dayeong] It's a slush fund probe.

01:04:56.442 --> 01:04:59.987 line:20%
And the Cabinet implored me
to fulfill my duties as the King.

01:05:00.071 --> 01:05:02.031 line:20%
[Jeongwoo] <i>We were simply speaking</i>
<i>on behalf of the public.</i>

01:05:02.115 --> 01:05:04.283 line:20%
Go and protect His Majesty.

01:05:04.367 --> 01:05:05.535 line:20%
[Jeongwoo] <i>It's your fault.</i>

01:05:07.870 --> 01:05:09.872 line:20%
Translated by Justin S. Kim.

01:05:21.175 --> 01:05:24.887 line:80%
PERFECT CROWN